card.name: Map Card
card.script:
on openCard create property playerPosition of this card if the playerPosition of this cd is empty then put "1,1" into the playerPosition of this card end if end openCard
on makeMap put the number of card buttons into numBtns repeat with x = numBtns down to 1 delete card button x end repeat put "0,0" into buttonName put "left:0" &newline& "top:0" &newline& "bottom:32" &newline& "right:32" into theBox repeat with y from 1 through 10 repeat with x from 1 through 16 put x &"," & y into buttonName create button buttonName set rectangle of last cd btn to theBox set style of last cd btn to "rectangle" set transparentColor to "red:0" &newline& "green:0" &newline& "blue:0" &newline& "alpha:0" set lineColor of last cd btn to transparentColor set fillColor of last cd btn to transparentColor set showName of last cd btn to false
add 32 to left of theBox add 32 to right of theBox end repeat put 0 into left of theBox put 32 into right of theBox add 32 to top of theBox add 32 to bottom of theBox end repeat
put "1,1" into the playerPosition of this card set icon of cd btn (playerPosition of this card) to 1000 end makeMap
on arrowKey theDirection put the playerPosition of this card into thePlayerPos if theDirection is "right" then set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 0 add 1 to item 1 of thePlayerPos set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 1000 else if theDirection is "left" then set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 0 subtract 1 from item 1 of thePlayerPos set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 1000 else if theDirection is "down" then set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 0 add 1 to item 2 of thePlayerPos set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 1000 else if theDirection is "up" then set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 0 subtract 1 from item 2 of thePlayerPos set icon of cd btn thePlayerPos to 1000 end if set the playerPosition of this card to thePlayerPos end arrowKey
on showplayer answer (the playerPosition of this card) end showplayer
